and <ENAMEX TYPE="ORGANIZATION">Technology</ENAMEX>, formerly the <ENAMEX TYPE="ORGANIZATION">Bureau of Standards</ENAMEX>
(a compilation, complete with numerical
coding, of <NUMEX TYPE="CARDINAL">some 190,000</NUMEX> populated places, locales,
