            The work is by no means at an end.  <ENAMEX TYPE="PER_DESC">Experts</ENAMEX>,
including Mr. <ENAMEX TYPE="PERSON">Payne</ENAMEX>, have estimated that there are
<NUMEX TYPE="CARDINAL">more than 3,500,000</NUMEX> current place names in the
<ENAMEX TYPE="GPE">U.S.</ENAMEX> Consider this figure in light of the fact that the
largest <ENAMEX TYPE="NATIONALITY">English</ENAMEX> <ENAMEX TYPE="PLANT">dictionary</ENAMEX>--now out of print--had
